name: 65 Million Clicks (BETA version)
description:
This game is a clicker game with a dinosaur theme.

It has a single player mode that is time-based that allows you to save your highest score, as well as multiplayer option which that allows you to compete with other people.

THIS IS A BETA VERSION OF THE GAME

Programming:
Bartosz Bielinski

Art:
Sam Cook - Assets
Kat Peverelle-Lee - Environment
David Olaleye - UI
